text: Timothy David Paine was born 8 December, 1984 in Hobart, Australia. He was an Australian cricketer who played 35 tests and 35 one-day internationals for Australia from 2010 to 2021 including captaining them in 23 tests from 2018 to 2021. He also played for Tasmania in the Sheffield Shield. ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers
